Frequently Asked Questions(FAQ) on Kohl's

How To Save Money At Kohl’s
With Kohl’s Cash, Kohl’s coupon codes and Kohl’s promo codes offered year round, you’ll never have a problem saving money at Kohl’s! Plus, a few times a year Kohl’s offers even more special sales for holidays like Black Friday. Coupon codes are sometimes valid during a site-wide sale for additional savings. Be wary of any Kohl’s mystery offers you may come across on social media, however - this fake is one example to look out for. 

Can I combine Kohl's coupons?
Yes, you can combine Kohl's coupons both online and in store. You can combine department-specific coupons and discount codes at Kohl’s; dollar-off coupons (like Kohl’s Cash and Kohl’s Rewards Cash); and sitewide discounts. When shopping online, a maximum of four discount codes can be applied to your Kohls.com order. If a promo code isn’t working, it may be because the item you are trying to purchase is on Kohl’s exclusions list.

How do I get Kohl's Mystery coupons?
Sign up for Kohl's emails. Every once in a while, you'll receive a Kohl's Mystery coupon code, good for 20%, 30% or 40% off site wide. Kohl's Mystery offers are generally valid only for a single day, so you'll need to act fast. To snag the offer, click on your Kohl's Mystery deal from the email. Go shopping. Then apply your Kohl's Mystery promo code at checkout. Your discount amount will be revealed and automatically applied to your order total. The Kohl's Myster offer cannot be used in stores -- it's an online-only deal. Got Kohl's Cash? You can use your Kohl's Cash on the same order as your Kohl's Mystery code.

Are there exclusions on Kohl's coupons?
Yes, sometimes. One of the main exclusions for Kohl's coupons and Kohl's promo codes is specific products. Some brands may not be eligible for Kohl's coupons, so if such an item is in your cart, your Kohl's coupon may not work. However, you can usually earn Kohl's rewards and Kohl's cash on these purchases -- and redeem Kohl's cash as well. In addition to excluded products, check your Kohl's coupon fine print for other exclusions, such as dates; your Kohl's coupon won't be valid past the date on the coupon. Finally, premium electronics are generally excluded from Kohl's coupons and Kohl's promo codes.

Do Kohl's Coupons Work on Instant Pots?
No. Instant Pot is one of the brands excluded for Kohl's coupons. To get a great deal on an Instant Pot at Kohl's, try shopping during peak sale times, such as Black Friday. Or, use earned Kohl's Cash against your order -- it's like an instant discount.

How Can I get Kohl's Coupons By Text?
Sign up for Kohl's coupons by text as well as other sale alerts by texting SAVEO20 to 56457. You'll receive a message to confirm your participation and then you'll be signed up. Within one day, you'll receive a text from Kohl's with a code to save on your very next purchase.

Does Kohl's give birthday coupons?
Yes. Kohl's rewards members get a special coupon on their birthday every year. Even better, the Kohl's rewards program is totally free to join.

What Is Kohl’s Cash?
You earn Kohl’s Cash during a Kohl’s Cash earn period -- that’s $10 in Kohl’s Cash for every $50 you spend usually, although offers might vary. When you shop in-store, you’ll receive Kohl’s Cash as a coupon; if you shop online, you’ll receive Kohl’s Cash in an email. Either way, if you have a Kohls.com shopping account, your Kohl’s Cash is automatically applied to your Kohl’s Wallet. You earn Kohl’s on anything -- and we mean anything -- there are no brand exclusions! Sometimes, Kohl's will offer extra Kohl's Cash on certain purchases. We've seen upwards of $50 Kohl's Cash for some big-ticket items.

How To Get Alerts For Kohl’s Offers And Deals
There are multiple ways to get alerted to deals at Kohl’s:
  • Sign up forKohl’s newsletter
  • Text SAVE02 to 56457 to receive SMS alerts of deals on your phone
  • Download the Kohl’s app 
  • Don’t forget to check your snail mail! 
  • Check out 15 more ways to save money at Kohl’s


    • How do I redeem a promo code on Kohls.com?
    Using a Kohl's coupon code is easy! At checkout, look under the “Order Summary” section on the top right of the page. There you’ll find a line for "Kohl's Cash & Promos" with an "apply" button. Click apply, and a window will pop up for entering the promo code or discount code. Up to 10 eligible codes and up to six Kohl’s Cash can be applied.


    How often do Kohl's coupons come out?
    Very often. Check the Kohl's website for the latest coupon offers. Generally, these coupons will have a promo code to be used if you're shopping online as well as a barcode if you're shopping in a store (you can show it on your phone at checkout if you don't have a printer for printable coupons). Kohl's Charge Card holders, meanwhile, get a special coupon roughly every month. Plus, if you're using Kohl's to make an Amazon return, the store is known to hand out a coupon to convince you to go shopping after making your return.


    How do I use multiple Kohl's promo codes?
    Stack up to four coupons, such as the ever-popular Kohl's 30% off coupon code with a free shipping code, a department specific code and Kohl's Cash during checkout to get the maximum savings on your purchase. 

    Does Kohl's take expired coupons?
    Officially, no. Your Kohl's coupon and your Kohl's Cash must be used by the deadline. This deadline will be printed on the coupon or specified online. If you try to use an expired Kohl's coupon or Kohl's cash online, the code will simply not work. If you try in store, the cashier won't be able to scan it.


    How do I sign up for rewards with Kohl's?
    Create an account with Kohl's to begin earning Kohl’s Rewards on all purchases both online and in store. After all, it's free! A link for the Kohl’s Rewards sign-up page can be found by clicking on "account" at the top right of any page on Kohls.com and selecting “Kohl’s Rewards.”

    How do Kohl's Rewards work?
    Kohl's no longer offers its former Yes2You rewards program and instead offers what it simply calls the Kohl's Rewards program. This program allows you to earn Kohl's Cash. Every time you shop, you'll earn 5% back, which will be issued to you in $5 Kohl's Cash increments. Then, you have 30 days to spend that Kohl's Cash. Kohl's rewards members also get a special Kohl's birthday gift (usually a coupon or limited-time promo code), as well as personalized perks throughout the year that let you earn Kohl's rewards faster. This is in addition to the Kohl's Cash you can earn during Kohl's Cash public events.

    Do Kohl's cardholders get free shipping?
    Yes, if you've acheived Kohl's MVC level status. Kohl's MVC shoppers get free shipping during certain times. Otherwise, you'll get free shipping if you place an order over the designated amount.

    What is Kohl's MVC?
    When you spend $600 or more on your Kohl’s Charge, you become a Most Valued Customer (MVC). As an MVC, you’ll receive extra perks like invites to free shipping events.

    What can I expect from the Kohl's Black Friday sale?
    The Kohl's Black Friday sale is one of the best. Expect Kohl's Black Friday deals to kick off almost a week before Thanksgiving -- but also expect some special Kohl's deals to be offered on Black Friday ONLY. Every year, Kohl's offers Black Friday deals on home goods, clothing, tech and more. Even better, the Black Friday sale includes Kohl's Cash offers -- expect Kohl's Cash back for every $50 you spend, as well as elevated Kohl's Cash when you buy certain items. Finally, check the Kohl's Black Friday ad and Kohl's website for a special Kohl's coupon code that's good only for the Black Friday sale. With all these savings combined, you'll often find that you can save a LOT during the Kohl's Black Friday sale. 

    What can I expect from the Kohl's Cyber Monday sale?
    More great deals and more Kohl's Cash earning opportunities. Plus, Kohl's will generally offer a Cyber Monday coupon code for online shoppers. 

    What is Kohl's return policy?
    Kohl's merchandise, excluding premium electronics, can be returned up to 180 days after the purchase date. Premium electronics have a 30-day return window and must include the original packaging and a valid receipt or account look-up. If a premium electronic was purchased between November 1 and December 25, it could be returned up to January 31 the following year. Items purchased in-store must also be returned in-store, but items purchased on Kohls.com can be returned to any Kohl’s location (you can also return online purchases by mail). Gift cards cannot be returned. 

    What is the Kohl's senior discount?
    The Kohl's senior discount is 15%, and it's avialable to customers 60 and up who shop in stores on Wednesdays. To get this special deal, you'll need to bring identification to verify your age. Note that, if you're using the Kohl's senior discount, you cannot then also use other percent-off coupons. If you're using the senior discount with Kohl's Cash or dollar-off coupons, those will be applied before the senior discount is applied. There are some exclusions to the senior discount, including select electronics, certain premium brands and other items.

    Does Kohl's have a student discount?
    Kohl's does not offer a student discount at this time, but you can always count on them for deep savings with coupons, promo codes and Kohl's Cash!

    About Kohl's
    Maxwell Kohl immigrated to the U.S. and opened a corner grocery store, Kohl's Food Stores, in 1927 in Milwaukee, Wisconsin. By 1962, the company branched out to open the department store Kohl's. They branded this department store as a middle option between high-end department stores and discount stores. Several celebrities, including Avril Lavigne, Jennifer Lopez, Paula DeAnda, Tony Hawk, and Marc Anthony, have sold exclusive branded clothing at Kohl's. In addition to clothing, Kohl's sells footwear, beauty products, jewelry, decor, housewares, toys, bedding, furniture, appliances, and electronics.

    Annual Sales
    Some of the holidays and events that Kohl's has annual sales for include Mother's Day, the 4th of July, Black Friday, and Christmas. Shoppers can save up to 70% during a sale. Coupon codes are sometimes valid during a site-wide sale for additional savings.

    Customer Service
    Customers can call 855-564-5705 to get in touch with the company's customer service. Shoppers who have concerns related to their Yes2You Rewards cards should contact 855-564-5751. The customer service line is open from 7 a.m. to 9 p.m. CT on Mondays through Saturdays and from 8 a.m. to 9 p.m. CT on Sundays.

    Live Chat
    On Kohl's "contact us" page, they have an "ask us" button. Customers can click this button to start an online chat with customer support. Just type "speak with person" to speak with a real person.

    App Info
    Kohl's has an app for Apple and Android users that they can use to place orders and view their rewards progress. The app can also send customers push notifications to alert them of new deals.

    Kohl's Card
    The Kohl's Card is a store credit card that customers can apply for. Cardholders receive exclusive monthly deals and a special anniversary offer every year. First-time cardholders receive 35% off their first purchase using the card. Customers who spend $600 by the end of the year receive a birthday gift and free shipping events.

    Email Newsletter Savings
    Kohl's gives a 15% off discount code for signing up for their email newsletter. Those who stay subscribed receive exclusive coupon codes, free shipping offers, and other savings opportunities.

    SMS Alerts
    Customers who sign up to receive SMS alerts from Kohl's receive a 15% off discount code. SMS subscribers receive around seven text messages a month. Customers must be at least 18 years old to sign up for SMS alerts.

    Senior Discounts
    Customers who are 60 years old or older can get a 15% discount in stores on Wednesdays. Employees will check IDs to confirm customers qualify for the senior discount. The Kohl's senior discount cannot be stacked with other promo codes.

    Military Discounts
    Kohl's offers in-store military discounts of 15% every Monday. Customers must show proof of military status, such as military ID, Form DD 214, or a state-issued ID that has veteran status on it. Both veterans and active-duty service members qualify for the Kohl's military discount. This discount cannot be stacked with other promo codes. Some additional exclusions apply.

    Rewards Program
    Customers who enroll in the Kohl's rewards program earn rewards points on all purchases. Members of the rewards program receive personalized perks and birthday gifts as well. Kohl's gives 5% in rewards on every dollar spent. During a Kohl's Cash earn period, customers earn an extra $10 Kohl's Cash for every $100 spent.

    Store Pickup Perks
    Kohl's rewards shoppers for choosing the store pickup option with $5 in Kohl's Cash. The company sometimes runs promos for additional savings on store pickup, such as $10 off on any order of at least $50. Kohl's sends the $5 Kohl's Cash reward through the confirmation email of a customer's order. Shoppers can only earn a $5 Kohl's Cash reward once every 24 hours.

    Free Shipping
    Kohl's provides free standard shipping on gift cards and orders of $75 or more. Excessively heavy packages may still have a shipping cost. Items that require special handling may also have shipping charges. Customers will be informed of what the shipping costs are before finalizing their orders.

    Price Match Policy
    Kohl's has a price match policy that will match in-store competitor prices and also the prices in other Kohl's locations. Advertised prices during the week of Thanksgiving and the week following Thanksgiving aren't eligible for being price matched. Customers must show a valid printout of the competitor product to a store associate for in-store price matching.

    White Glove Delivery
    Kohl's provides white glove delivery for residents in the contiguous U.S. when an item is too heavy or too large to be shipped through their regular carriers. The delivery workers will bring it inside the home and unpack it for the customer.
